                    h1.agent-name Susan Ellsworth, Realtor
                    p.agent-bio Originally from New York, Susan moved to Titusville in 1980 and fell in love with the small town feel here. Her experience working on the United States Space Program for over 20 years gave her a passion for working in the area. Drawing on her Human Resources, Finance and Technology areas of expertise, she provides excellent customer service with a strong focus on relationships and budgeting/financing a new home.<br><br> Honesty and integrity, along with determination and dedication, are philosophies that Susan strives for in all aspects of her life. Applying these principles to her business has allowed her to transition these skills into a successful real estate career. Her background has given her real estate business a high level of experience, leadership, and professionalism, and her optimistic and friendly personality makes her a pleasure for her clients to work with.<br><br> Susan enjoys spending time with her family and friends, going to the beach, and traveling.
